Una xa mda'a snan tsaan tlu'hue can', Ndiose mxu'hua ñi cusya 'in yu lo' mdyiton yu, ndyijyin ya' ytsen nchgaa nu na'an cha' can'.
A cunta mxiycui' cunaan tlyu can' 'in 'ni la can' si'yana lo'o cha' siye' chcui' cha' nu tnu lo' taja 'in Ndiose, lo' jui cha' cuiya' 'in si'yana culo tñan tsani' tucua yla ntsu'hui tucua coo'.
