lo' si'yana nguitsen yu, can' cha' tijyo' ti' ndon yu na'an yu se'en ndiquin can', lo' nchcui' yu: Ti'i ca xu'hue, ti'i ca xu'hue Babilonia, quichen tlyu nu tla 'a cha' 'in can', si'yana ni' sca braa ti ngujlyo na.
Nga'an sca cha' 'in ste' ñi lo'o sii' ndan ñi, lo' nchcui' na: Scati Ree nu tlyu lati, scati X'nan nchgaa tucui.
